<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>战区</title><link>https://www.twz.com</link><description>防御世界的强大进攻。</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 13:12:51 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>海军绞尽脑汁维持航母的生存计划</title><link>https://www.twz.com/sea/navy-juggles-its-aircraft-carrier-plans-to-stay-afloat</link><description>&lt;p&gt;一艘航母在起火前就已经疲惫不堪，另一艘航母的使用寿命第二次延长，而第三艘航母的交付则被推迟。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/sea/navy-juggles-its-aircraft-carrier-plans-to-stay-afloat"&gt;海军努力维持其航空母舰计划以保持漂浮的帖子&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;“战区”&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 23:50:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/sea/navy-juggles-its-aircraft-carrier-plans-to-stay-afloat</guid></item><item><title>特朗普不再希望盟友派遣军舰打开霍尔木兹海峡（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/trump-no-longer-wants-allies-to-send-warships-to-open-the-strait-of-hormuz</link><description>&lt;p&gt;在盟友拒绝他向该海峡派遣军舰的要求一天后，特朗普宣布“我们不需要任何人的帮助！”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/trump-no-longer-wants-allies-to-send-warships-to-open-the-strait-of-hormuz"&gt;特朗普不再希望盟友派遣军舰打开霍尔木兹海峡（更新）的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 23:17:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/trump-no-longer-wants-allies-to-send-warships-to-open-the-strait-of-hormuz</guid></item><item><title>海军 E-2D 鹰眼战斗机似乎正赶往中东</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/navy-e-2d-hawkeye-radar-planes-appear-to-be-rushing-to-the-middle-east</link><description>&lt;p&gt;E-2D 是美国最有能力发现正在对海湾阿拉伯国家造成严重破坏的无人机和其他低空飞行的伊朗威胁的平台。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;后&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/navy-e-2d-hawkeye-radar-planes-appear-to-be-rushing-to-the-middle-east"&gt;海军 E-2D 鹰眼战机似乎正赶往中东&lt;/a&gt;首次出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;中。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 22:50:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/navy-e-2d-hawkeye-radar-planes-appear-to-be-rushing-to-the-middle-east</guid></item><item><title>日本 EC-2 电子战喷气机，堪称世界上最丑的飞机，刚刚首飞</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/the-worlds-ugliest-airplane-just-flew-for-the-first-time</link><description>&lt;p&gt;在军用飞机设计日益同质化的世界中，鸭嘴兽般的川崎 EC-2 是一个彻底的异类。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/the-worlds-ugliest-airplane-just-flew-for-the-first-time"&gt;日本的 EC-2 电子战喷气式飞机，可以说是世界上最丑的飞机，刚刚首次飞行，&lt;/a&gt;该帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 19:08:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/the-worlds-ugliest-airplane-just-flew-for-the-first-time</guid></item><item><title>盟友拒绝特朗普向霍尔木兹海峡派遣军舰的要求（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/allies-push-back-on-trumps-demand-they-send-warships-to-strait-of-hormuz</link><description>&lt;p&gt;德国周一断然拒绝了特朗普关于北约盟国派遣海军舰艇帮助保护这条战略水道航运的要求。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/allies-push-back-on-trumps-demand-they-send-warships-to-strait-of-hormuz"&gt;盟友拒绝特朗普向霍尔木兹海峡派遣军舰的要求（更新）&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Mar 2026 23:49:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/allies-push-back-on-trumps-demand-they-send-warships-to-strait-of-hormuz</guid></item><item><title>携带新旧干扰吊舱混合负载的 EA-18G 咆哮者正在执行伊朗任务</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/ea-18g-growler-with-split-load-of-new-and-old-jamming-pods-seen-supporting-iran-strikes</link><description>&lt;p&gt;五角大楼的一份报告称，尽管新吊舱正在被用于活跃的冲突中，但它们仍然存在严重的初期问题。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/ea-18g-growler-with-split-load-of-new-and-old-jamming-pods-seen-supporting-iran-strikes"&gt;携带新旧干扰吊舱混合负载的 EA-18G 咆哮者飞机正在执行伊朗任务，&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Mar 2026 21:53:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/ea-18g-growler-with-split-load-of-new-and-old-jamming-pods-seen-supporting-iran-strikes</guid></item><item><title>以色列声称摧毁“伊朗力量一号”</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/israel-claims-destruction-of-iran-force-one</link><description>&lt;p&gt;去年以色列空袭期间，伊朗政府的空客 A340 是伊朗国营飞机逃往阿曼的一部分。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/israel-claims-destruction-of-iran-force-one"&gt;以色列声称摧毁“伊朗一号”的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;“战区”&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Mar 2026 16:40:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/israel-claims-destruction-of-iran-force-one</guid></item><item><title>以色列和美国官员表示战争可能再持续三周（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/israeli-and-u-s-officials-indicate-war-could-go-on-for-another-three-weeks</link><description>&lt;p&gt;特朗普表示，他还没有准备好达成协议，而以色列则表示仍有数千个目标需要打击。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/israeli-and-u-s-officials-indicate-war-could-go-on-for-another-three-weeks"&gt;以色列和美国官员表示战争可能再持续三周（更新）&lt;/a&gt;一文首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;“战区”&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Mar 2026 02:47:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/israeli-and-u-s-officials-indicate-war-could-go-on-for-another-three-weeks</guid></item><item><title>美国海军分配到中东的扫雷舰已转移到太平洋（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/sea/u-s-navy-minesweepers-assigned-to-middle-east-have-been-moved-to-pacific</link><description>&lt;p&gt;在中东承担扫雷任务的三艘濒海战斗舰中的两艘刚刚出现在马来西亚。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/sea/u-s-navy-minesweepers-assigned-to-middle-east-have-been-moved-to-pacific"&gt;分配到中东的美国海军扫雷舰已转移到太平洋（更新）&lt;/a&gt;后首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 15 Mar 2026 21:05:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/sea/u-s-navy-minesweepers-assigned-to-middle-east-have-been-moved-to-pacific</guid></item><item><title>地堡谈话：让我们谈谈本周我们做过和没有涵盖的所有事情</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/bunker-talk-lets-talk-about-all-the-things-we-did-and-didnt-cover-this-week-183</link><description>&lt;p&gt;应该买通用的！&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/bunker-talk-lets-talk-about-all-the-things-we-did-and-didnt-cover-this-week-183"&gt;《地堡谈话：让我们谈谈本周我们做过和没有涵盖的所有事情》&lt;/a&gt;一文首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 22:47:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/bunker-talk-lets-talk-about-all-the-things-we-did-and-didnt-cover-this-week-183</guid></item></channel></rss>